column4:
Functional Features: This object is a double-layer industrial shelf, used to provide material storage space in scenarios such as warehousing and workshops. It can classify and place tools, components, finished products, etc. Its application scenarios include cargo storage in e-commerce warehouses, parts placement in automobile workshops, and material organization in small factories. It can effectively utilize vertical space, increase storage capacity and the convenience of material access, and help standardize the management of warehousing and production areas.
Visual Features: The main frame is in blue and red colors, and the shelves are dark gray. The material is metal (frame and shelves), and the surface treatment shows the solid texture of metal. The coating is uniform and has certain wear resistance. The structural design is concise and stable, and the double-layer layout is layered and distinct against the black background. The color matching highlights the practicality and recognizability of industrial equipment.

Functional Features: This object is a three-layer industrial shelf, used to provide multi-layer material storage space in scenarios such as warehousing and production workshops. It can classify and store tools, components, finished products or raw materials. Its application scenarios include layered storage of goods in e-commerce warehouses, parts organization in mechanical workshops, and material placement in small warehousing centers. It can efficiently utilize vertical space, increase storage capacity and the convenience of material access, and help orderly manage warehousing and production areas.
Visual Features: The main frame is in blue and red colors, and the shelves are dark gray. The material is metal (frame and shelves), and the surface treatment shows the solid texture of metal. The coating is uniform and wear-resistant. The three-layer structural design is concise and stable, with clear layers against the black background. The color matching highlights the practicality and recognizability of industrial equipment.

Functional Features: This object is a three-layer industrial shelf, used to provide multi-layer material storage and classification space in scenarios such as warehousing and workshops. It can place tools, components, finished products, etc. Its application scenarios include layered storage of goods in e-commerce warehouses, parts organization in mechanical workshops, and material placement in small warehousing centers. It can efficiently utilize vertical space, increase storage capacity and the convenience of material access, and help orderly manage warehousing and production areas.
Visual Features: The main frame is silver-gray (metal material) with blue edges, and the shelves are silver-gray metal. The surface treatment shows the solid texture of metal, with uniform and wear-resistant coating. The three-layer structural design is concise and stable, with clear layers against the black background. The color matching of silver-gray and blue highlights the practicality and recognizability of industrial equipment.
